<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.7.7">
<l>vantaruḷi yeṉṉeñ ciṭaṅkoṇṭa vāṉavar koḻuntē yulakukkōr</l>
<l>muntait tāytantai yēmuḻu veḻulaku muṇṭāy</l>
<l>cento ḻilavar vēta vēḷviyaṟāc cirīvara maṅkalanakar</l>
<l>antamil pukaḻā yaṭiyēṉai yakaṟṟēlē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Sprout of the celestials who graciously came [and] took a place in my heart, of old</l>
<l>sole mother [and] father to the world, you who have swallowed all the seven worlds,</l>
<l>you of unending fame in the city of Cirīvaramaṅkalam where the vedic sacrifices</l>
<l>of those with refined work do not cease, do not forsake me, [your] servant.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
